&gt; POST /someURI                  update resource state;
&gt; &lt;details&gt;                      /someUri goes to &quot;.../ready&quot; state
&gt;  ...                                
&gt;  &lt;clientViewOfState&gt;
&gt;     &quot;http://.../initial&quot;  --&gt;        
&gt;  &lt;/clientViewOfState&gt;
&gt; &lt;/details&gt;
&gt;                                          
&gt;                           &lt;--  200 OK gets lost         
