&gt; client re-sends:
&gt; POST /someURI                            
&gt; &lt;details&gt;                      server detects conflict;
&gt;   ...                          informs client of what its view is
&gt;   &lt;clientViewOfState&gt;
&gt;      &quot;http://.../initial&quot; --&gt;        
